metadata.description: Empowered Woman unlocks private club access, exclusive drops, experiences and allows you exclusive access to the individuals the owner of the NFT has sponsored along with access to our facilities in the metaverse! The owners will be given VIP access to all these and more!Empowered Women unites women to become independent and brings forth positivity towards women's education, social justice and equality! Our cause is to assure women's rights to education, prevention of social pressures towards backwards cultures leading to women oppression and abuse, and align women from all walks of life towards economic empowerment through education.
